SELECT QuantumCircuits.circuit_name, Errors.error_type FROM QuantumCircuits JOIN ErrorRecords ON QuantumCircuits.circuit_id = ErrorRecords.circuit_id JOIN Errors ON ErrorRecords.error_id = Errors.error_id;
SELECT circuit_name, circuit_description FROM QuantumCircuits WHERE circuit_description LIKE '%QFT%';
SELECT circuit_id, MAX(error_probability) AS max_probability FROM ErrorRecords JOIN Errors ON ErrorRecords.error_id = Errors.error_id GROUP BY circuit_id;

SELECT circuit_id, circuit_name FROM quantum_circuits;

SELECT gate_name, gate_type, qubit_id FROM gates ORDER BY gate_id DESC;
SELECT measurement_id, syndrome_result FROM syndrome_measurement WHERE correction_id = 1;

SELECT circuit_name, circuit_description FROM quantum_circuits WHERE circuit_id IN (1, 2, 3);
SELECT q.qubit_name, g.gate_name, e.error_description FROM qubits q JOIN gates g ON q.qubit_id = g.qubit_id JOIN error_correction e ON g.gate_id = e.gate_id;
SELECT g.gate_type, s.syndrome_result FROM gates g JOIN error_correction e ON g.gate_id = e.gate_id JOIN syndrome_measurement s ON e.correction_id = s.correction_id WHERE g.gate_type = 'Hadamard';

SELECT q.qubit_name, g.gate_name, e.error_description, s.syndrome_result FROM qubits q JOIN gates g ON q.qubit_id = g.qubit_id JOIN error_correction e ON g.gate_id = e.gate_id JOIN syndrome_measurement s ON e.correction_id = s.correction_id WHERE q.qubit_name LIKE 'qubit%' AND g.gate_type = 'CNOT';
